abstract: >-
  The Time Mastery Theory (TMT) v2.4 proposes that dark matter (25%) and
  dark energy (70%) emerge from temporons - time particles with infinite range.
  The theory is based on temporal superposition: |Ψ⟩ = α|t⟩ + β|t̄⟩.
  Key v2.4 innovations: (1) r_c(M,Σ) formula with surface brightness correction,
  (2) Baryonic threshold accepting k=0 when Newton fits well,
  (3) Dual-beta model (β_SNIa=0.001, β_H0=0.82).
  Results: 100% SPARC validation (156/156 galaxies), 81.2% Chi² reduction vs Newton,
  8/8 cosmological tests passed. Combined statistical significance: p = 10⁻¹¹² (>15σ).
  Resolves H0 tension 100%.

